WEBVTT

00:30.489 --> 00:33.033
FABULOUS GODMOTHER:
Once upon a time...

00:35.244 --> 00:37.663
...there was
an old-fashioned kingdom

00:37.747 --> 00:39.957
bound by tradition.

00:41.751 --> 00:44.211
Here, everyone had
a part to play,

00:44.295 --> 00:47.423
and they played it
without question.

00:47.506 --> 00:49.967
Little did they know,

00:50.050 --> 00:54.180
their world was about to change.

00:56.599 --> 00:59.977
But until it did, y'all...

01:00.060 --> 01:02.271
this village
of hardworking citizens

01:02.354 --> 01:06.233
moved to the same beat
day after day,

01:06.317 --> 01:09.820
generation after generation.

01:36.931 --> 01:38.182
for a better way

01:38.265 --> 01:40.226
-

01:40.309 --> 01:43.854
of the rhythm nation

01:43.938 --> 01:48.651
the rhythm nation

01:48.734 --> 01:50.653
FABULOUS GODMOTHER:
And over here

01:50.736 --> 01:54.365
is where our story begins,
at the humble home

01:54.448 --> 01:56.909
of a practical woman
named Vivian,

01:56.992 --> 01:59.036
who was alone again

01:59.119 --> 02:02.581
after the death
of her second husband.

02:02.665 --> 02:08.420
a better way of life

02:10.381 --> 02:12.383
Vivian's daughters:

02:12.466 --> 02:16.011
the obnoxious Malvolia

02:16.095 --> 02:19.139
and the self-absorbed Narissa.

02:19.223 --> 02:20.933
She cray.

02:21.016 --> 02:25.062
-

02:25.145 --> 02:28.566
of the rhythm nation

02:28.649 --> 02:31.318
-Um, yeah.

02:31.402 --> 02:33.237
They can be a lot.

02:33.320 --> 02:34.947
I'm winning!

02:35.030 --> 02:36.991
-Whee!

02:38.742 --> 02:40.786
And down here,

02:40.870 --> 02:43.414
in this dingy basement,

02:43.497 --> 02:45.624
the stepdaughter, Ella.

02:45.708 --> 02:49.378
Or, as her stepsisters
call her, Cinderella,

02:49.461 --> 02:53.007
because her skin
was often besmirched by cinders

02:53.090 --> 02:55.885
and her stepsisters
were not that clever.

02:55.968 --> 02:58.554
Right now,
she's dreaming of a world

02:58.637 --> 03:02.266
in which she can live her life
any way she wants.

03:02.349 --> 03:05.019
Uh, watch it now. You about
to roll over on that...

03:05.102 --> 03:07.104
-...pin.

03:09.273 --> 03:11.233
the future holds

03:11.317 --> 03:15.529
your head up to the sky

03:15.613 --> 03:17.740
cause you tears

03:21.911 --> 03:23.871
unless you try

03:23.954 --> 03:25.706
you gotta be bad

03:25.789 --> 03:28.918
you gotta be wiser

03:29.001 --> 03:31.420
you gotta be tough

03:33.505 --> 03:35.925
you gotta be calm

03:45.851 --> 03:49.730
We are a part
of the rhythm nation

03:51.857 --> 03:54.360
-

03:54.443 --> 03:57.613
if you can't stand the pace

03:57.696 --> 03:59.990
-

04:03.285 --> 04:07.998
staring you in the face

04:11.710 --> 04:14.004
you gotta be bold

04:16.256 --> 04:18.676
you gotta be tough

04:20.260 --> 04:22.721
you gotta be calm

04:35.025 --> 04:36.610
-Smashed it!
-Perfectamundo.

04:36.694 --> 04:39.154
Take that, birds.

04:39.238 --> 04:41.198
Good morning,
my beady-eyed friends.

04:41.281 --> 04:42.950
You hungry?

04:43.033 --> 04:44.201
-Oh, yeah.
-Nod your head, mates.

04:44.284 --> 04:46.412
-All she hears is squeaks.
-Mm. Come to papa.

04:46.495 --> 04:47.746
- Ooh.

04:50.165 --> 04:52.418
you gotta be bold

04:52.501 --> 04:54.545
gotta be wiser

04:54.628 --> 04:56.839
you gotta be tough

04:56.922 --> 04:58.716
gotta be stronger

04:58.799 --> 05:01.385
you gotta be calm

05:01.468 --> 05:03.137
keep it together

05:10.811 --> 05:13.147
-

05:13.230 --> 05:15.190
a better way of life?

