Stepmother.

1:22:25.566 --> 1:22:26.609
I can provide for us.

1:22:26.692 --> 1:22:27.735
Don't be so stupid.

1:22:27.818 --> 1:22:29.278
Who taught you
to think that way?

1:22:29.362 --> 1:22:31.447
