throw away this opportunity.

1:22:31.530 --> 1:22:32.740
Go back to him.

1:22:32.823 --> 1:22:35.826
It's too late.

1:22:35.910 --> 1:22:37.828
He's marrying someone else.

1:22:37.912 --> 1:22:39.538
It's over.

1:22:45.419 --> 1:22:47.046
Fine.

1:22:51.634 --> 1:22:53.803
Then I'm taking you to Thomas,

1:22:53.886 --> 1:22:56.597
and I'm giving you to him today.

1:22:57.682 --> 1:22:59.892
I would rather die.

