1:27:19.068 --> 1:27:20.611
The crown changed you.

1:27:20.694 --> 1:27:23.489
You're so worried
to look a fool.

1:27:23.572 --> 1:27:26.825
So obsessed with your
reputation, with your legacy.

1:27:26.909 --> 1:27:28.911
