1:27:28.994 --> 1:27:31.163
It causes me
a great deal of stress.

1:27:31.246 --> 1:27:33.248
Do you think you're the only
person who feels stress?

1:27:33.332 --> 1:27:35.751
God, try being your bloody wife.

1:27:35.834 --> 1:27:39.421
It is utterly exhausting to sit
next to you and just smile

1:27:39.505 --> 1:27:41.423
as if I were nothing more
than a prop,

1:27:41.507 --> 1:27:44.259
my voice completely silenced.

1:27:44.343 --> 1:27:46.428
I mean, what I wouldn't give
to say, "You're wrong,"

1:27:46.512 --> 1:27:48.389
in front of the entire kingdom.

1:27:48.472 --> 1:27:49.974
Bea...

1:27:50.057 --> 1:27:52.101
you're being unreasonable now.

1:27:53.894 --> 1:27:56.021
Well, if you say so.

1:27:56.105 --> 1:27:58.107
After all, you're the king.

1:28:00.109 --> 1:28:02.486
Can't be any other opinions
other than yours.

1:28:07.366 --> 1:28:10.411
