there's never a guarantee

1:28:10.494 --> 1:28:13.414
with a couple in our position.

1:28:13.497 --> 1:28:15.666
But we had love, Rowan.

1:28:15.749 --> 1:28:17.835
We had it.

1:28:17.918 --> 1:28:19.545
And now...

1:28:21.964 --> 1:28:24.174
