1:28:31.849 --> 1:28:33.475
Hello.

1:28:36.395 --> 1:28:38.022
I'm ready.

1:28:46.280 --> 1:28:48.699
You summoned me, Your Highness?

1:28:50.617 --> 1:28:52.911
We can't have
a regular conversation

1:28:52.995 --> 1:28:54.830
like a normal father and son,
can we?

1:28:54.913 --> 1:28:56.623
No, no.

1:28:56.707 --> 1:28:58.584
To satisfy your power trip,
you have to sit there

1:28:58.667 --> 1:29:00.586
on your slightly too tall
throne.

1:29:00.669 --> 1:29:02.046
You-you belittle me in your...

1:29:02.129 --> 1:29:05.424
your-your king voice, yes.

1:29:05.507 --> 1:29:07.760
All because you're so insecure

1:29:07.843 --> 1:29:10.345
with your legacy that you
have to control my every move.

1:29:10.429 --> 1:29:12.014
Now, I ask you,

1:29:12.097 --> 1:29:14.266
does that sound
like a strong leader to you?

1:29:14.349 --> 1:29:15.726
ROWAN:
Robert...

1:29:17.394 --> 1:29:19.354
I was wrong.

1:29:27.571 --> 1:29:30.991
I, King Rowan...

1:29:32.284 --> 1:29:33.952
Am I doing the king voice?

1:29:34.036 --> 1:29:35.621
A little bit.
You can't help yourself.

1:29:43.629 --> 1:29:45.964
Go find the owner
of this glass slipper.

1:29:46.048 --> 1:29:50.177
And if she'll take you back,
then marry her.

1:29:50.260 --> 1:29:51.887
Or don't.

1:29:53.430 --> 1:29:54.973
It's your life, son.

1:29:55.057 --> 1:29:56.600
Wh-Why the sudden
change of heart?

1:29:56.683 --> 1:29:59.728
Well, definitely
wasn't your mum.

1:30:00.896 --> 1:30:02.815
-Go on, leave now.
-

1:30:02.898 --> 1:30:04.608
Be bold.

1:30:13.325 --> 1:30:15.119
you won't believe

1:30:16.578 --> 1:30:18.330
at the ball

1:30:18.413 --> 1:30:20.916
for a pretty young lady

1:30:20.999 --> 1:30:23.043
who then turned out to be

1:30:23.127 --> 1:30:24.962
see, at the end of the night

1:30:25.045 --> 1:30:27.589
she left no name

1:30:27.673 --> 1:30:29.133
just a shoe made of glass

1:30:29.216 --> 1:30:30.926
for the girl

1:30:31.009 --> 1:30:33.387
no buckles, no laces

1:30:33.470 --> 1:30:35.264
-ROSEMARY:

1:30:35.347 --> 1:30:37.266
does it look like this?

1:30:37.349 --> 1:30:39.184
swing and a miss

1:30:39.268 --> 1:30:41.854
could my foot be right?

1:30:41.937 --> 1:30:44.731
a canoe, ma'am, way too tight

1:30:44.815 --> 1:30:46.859
that I birthed

1:30:56.535 --> 1:30:57.703
-Mm.
-

1:30:57.786 --> 1:30:59.246
That is too bad.

1:30:59.329 --> 1:31:01.206
But I like those vocal runs.

1:31:03.375 --> 1:31:06.170
who needs convincing

1:31:06.253 --> 1:31:08.505
with the ring-a-ding-ding

1:31:08.589 --> 1:31:11.300
in the shoe that goes bling

1:31:11.383 --> 1:31:14.219
tell it to your future king.

1:31:18.056 --> 1:31:19.099
Not her.

1:31:24.771 --> 1:31:25.772
Worth a try.

1:31:29.151 --> 1:31:30.402
