1:32:02.809 --> 1:32:04.686
You don't say.

1:32:06.688 --> 1:32:08.649
We're not going to find her.

1:32:08.732 --> 1:32:10.651
-We should just go home.
-I can't.

1:32:10.734 --> 1:32:13.111
I have to let her know
that it's possible between us.

1:32:13.195 --> 1:32:16.573
It's a beautiful thing
how much you love her.

1:32:16.657 --> 1:32:19.910
-You crying, Hench?
-So what if I am?

1:32:19.993 --> 1:32:22.120
Would that we all have
what Robert has.

1:32:22.204 --> 1:32:25.165
I mean, what is life

1:32:25.249 --> 1:32:27.251
if you're not with
the person you love?

1:32:27.334 --> 1:32:28.961
Right?

1:32:29.044 --> 1:32:31.755
Otherwise, we might as well
just close our eyes

1:32:31.838 --> 1:32:36.760
and take the ol' mud nap,
because...

1:32:36.843 --> 1:32:39.221
nothing else matters.

1:32:41.014 --> 1:32:43.100
So we find her, then.

1:32:43.183 --> 1:32:44.685
Robert, where did you see her

1:32:44.768 --> 1:32:46.311
the last time
you went searching?

