You all right?

1:34:38.215 --> 1:34:40.425
-What are you doing here?
-Are you hurt?

1:34:40.509 --> 1:34:42.219
No, I-I'm fine.
I just really have to...

1:34:42.302 --> 1:34:43.595
Good. I've been looking for you.

1:34:43.678 --> 1:34:44.971
Why?

1:34:45.055 --> 1:34:46.848
I have something
that I want to say.

1:34:46.932 --> 1:34:48.350
You inspired me.

1:34:48.433 --> 1:34:49.893
Me?

1:34:49.976 --> 1:34:51.770
It never occurred to me
that I could choose

1:34:51.853 --> 1:34:53.480
the course of my own life.

1:34:53.563 --> 1:34:56.566
See, I-I always felt
that it was written for me.

1:34:56.650 --> 1:34:59.778
But watching you, I-I realized
that anything is possible.

1:34:59.861 --> 1:35:01.655
That's so sweet.

1:35:01.738 --> 1:35:03.907
I'm just really in a hurry.
If we could talk about it...

1:35:03.990 --> 1:35:06.701
I realize now that I can have
a life that is all mine.

1:35:06.785 --> 1:35:08.829
Great. This is gonna
be a lengthy discussion.

1:35:08.912 --> 1:35:12.249
What I'm trying to say
is that I choose me.

1:35:12.332 --> 1:35:13.708
Hmm?

1:35:13.792 --> 1:35:16.795
God, this is not coming out
how I wanted it to.

1:35:18.547 --> 1:35:20.465
I don't have to be king.

1:35:20.549 --> 1:35:22.092
It is not what I want anymore.

1:35:22.175 --> 1:35:23.427
You are.

1:35:23.510 --> 1:35:26.221
So, what I'm saying is

1:35:26.304 --> 1:35:28.723
choosing me is choosing us.

1:35:30.350 --> 1:35:32.936
That is, as long as
you feel the same way.

1:35:36.606 --> 1:35:37.774
Your silence is...

1:35:55.542 --> 1:35:57.461
That was the most romantic
moment of my life.

1:35:57.544 --> 1:35:58.628
Same.

1:35:58.712 --> 1:36:00.922
-I mean, you rode up on a horse.
-I did.

1:36:01.006 --> 1:36:01.965
It was really cool.

1:36:02.048 --> 1:36:03.592
You look so beautiful.

1:36:03.675 --> 1:36:05.177
-You look so handsome.
-Thank you.

1:36:05.260 --> 1:36:07.262
Oh, uh, got to go.
I need you to

1:36:07.345 --> 1:36:09.639
put me on that horse and get me
to the market square, please.

1:36:09.723 --> 1:36:11.141
-Okay.
-What? No.

1:36:11.224 --> 1:36:12.767
-No? Okay. I'm sorry. Yes.
-I can walk. It's-it's faster.

1:36:12.851 --> 1:36:14.019
But thank you.
That's really nice.

1:36:16.563 --> 1:36:19.316
-ROWAN Beatrice!

1:36:20.775 --> 1:36:22.360
Beatrice!

1:36:22.444 --> 1:36:25.489
What fresh hell is this?

1:36:25.572 --> 1:36:26.531
Beatrice!

1:36:26.615 --> 1:36:29.534
It is I, your knight
in shining armor.

1:36:32.871 --> 1:36:35.999
You can't be serious.

1:36:36.082 --> 1:36:39.503
Darling, suspend
what you know to be true.

1:36:39.586 --> 1:36:41.588
Just...

1:36:42.672 --> 1:36:44.883
Just-just go with it.

1:36:46.968 --> 1:36:48.970
Oh, no. He's gonna sing.

1:36:52.682 --> 1:36:54.100
-

1:36:56.102 --> 1:36:58.271
You really don't
have to do this.

1:36:58.355 --> 1:36:59.648
But I do, darling.

1:36:59.731 --> 1:37:01.399
This is exactly what you wanted.

1:37:01.483 --> 1:37:02.901
Nope. No. Not really.

1:37:10.242 --> 1:37:11.785
Everybody.

1:37:13.995 --> 1:37:15.705
-

1:37:15.789 --> 1:37:17.415
-Oh, my God.
-

1:37:17.499 --> 1:37:19.084
Okay,
that's enough. That's enough.

1:37:19.167 --> 1:37:20.168
Yes. Thank you.

1:37:21.878 --> 1:37:22.879
Oh. Big finish.

1:37:38.728 --> 1:37:42.899
-

