BEATRICE:

1:37:47.904 --> 1:37:49.781
-Oh, my love.

1:37:50.991 --> 1:37:52.784
Oh. Can I come up?

1:37:52.867 --> 1:37:54.160
Yes, if you can get
your armor off.

1:38:07.799 --> 1:38:09.426
Pack your bags.

1:38:10.802 --> 1:38:12.637
-Huh?
-

1:38:12.721 --> 1:38:13.722
