-

1:38:19.352 --> 1:38:20.979
-ROBERT: Mother? Father?
-In here,

1:38:21.062 --> 1:38:22.397
being immortalized.

1:38:22.480 --> 1:38:24.524
There's someone
I would like you to meet.

1:38:24.608 --> 1:38:26.484
-I'm Ella.
-Now, how lovely.

1:38:26.568 --> 1:38:29.070
Oh, yeah, I remember you.

1:38:29.154 --> 1:38:30.822
You're the statue girl.

1:38:30.905 --> 1:38:32.282
That wasn't me.

1:38:32.365 --> 1:38:34.326
Yes, it was.
I'm good with faces.

1:38:35.535 --> 1:38:36.703
So, do I have
a wedding to prepare?

1:38:36.786 --> 1:38:38.455
I mean, no pressure,

1:38:38.538 --> 1:38:40.123
but there's an absurd amount
of pastries

1:38:40.206 --> 1:38:41.750
left over from that ball.

1:38:41.833 --> 1:38:43.793
No, no, we're not in a rush
to get married.

1:38:43.877 --> 1:38:45.670
Uh, instead, we're going to
travel the world together.

1:38:45.754 --> 1:38:47.589
Ah. Hmm.

1:38:47.672 --> 1:38:49.090
I'm sorry if
my decision disrupts

1:38:49.174 --> 1:38:50.800
-your plans for succession.
-Well, that's all right.

1:38:50.884 --> 1:38:54.929
It just so happens I share blood
with another who, one day,

1:38:55.013 --> 1:38:57.932
will be the greatest leader
the realm has ever known.

1:38:58.016 --> 1:38:59.768
Hear that, Gwen?

1:39:01.269 --> 1:39:02.812
What's happening?

1:39:02.896 --> 1:39:04.689
-Gwen, my darling girl.
-

1:39:04.773 --> 1:39:09.277
