to inherit the crown, hmm?

1:39:09.361 --> 1:39:10.987
Don't stab me in my sleep.

1:39:12.322 --> 1:39:14.741
I... shall be king?

1:39:14.824 --> 1:39:15.992
Eh, queen.

1:39:16.076 --> 1:39:18.203
I'll take it.

1:39:18.286 --> 1:39:19.496
Good.

1:39:23.375 --> 1:39:25.877
Just so we're clear,
I'm going to rule the land?

1:39:25.960 --> 1:39:28.129
-Yes.
-Okay.

1:39:29.506 --> 1:39:30.840
And everyone heard that?

1:39:30.924 --> 1:39:32.258
-We did. Yes.
-Yes. -Yeah. Mm-hmm.

1:39:32.342 --> 1:39:34.219
Oh!

1:39:34.302 --> 1:39:36.471
So many ideas!

1:39:36.554 --> 1:39:39.516
Like... Oh, I don't know
where to begin!

1:39:39.599 --> 1:39:41.142
Oh, good.
Can I take this crown off?

1:39:41.226 --> 1:39:42.686
-Yes.
-Shall we have some tea?

1:39:44.104 --> 1:39:45.814
GWEN:
It is my honor

1:39:45.897 --> 1:39:49.275
to guide this kingdom forward
into a new era.

1:39:49.359 --> 1:39:52.320
And to pay my deepest respects
to my brother,

1:39:52.404 --> 1:39:55.156
Prince Robert, and his new...

1:39:56.866 --> 1:39:58.493
What are we calling you?

1:39:58.576 --> 1:40:00.036
Well...

1:40:00.120 --> 1:40:02.163
I mean, we don't have to put
a label on it.

1:40:02.247 --> 1:40:03.873
Just... in love?

1:40:03.957 --> 1:40:05.125
I don't know.

1:40:05.208 --> 1:40:06.918
In love?

1:40:07.001 --> 1:40:08.962
Yeah.

1:40:09.045 --> 1:40:10.797
In love.

1:40:10.880 --> 1:40:13.800
And his new love, Ella!

1:40:26.146 --> 1:40:28.022
Ella.

1:40:28.106 --> 1:40:31.735
I believe this belongs to you.

1:40:31.818 --> 1:40:33.528
My mother's brooch.

1:40:33.611 --> 1:40:35.822
I thought it could inspire you
on your voyage.

1:40:35.905 --> 1:40:37.323
Thank you.

1:40:38.742 --> 1:40:40.577
All right, that's enough mirth.
Celebration's over.

1:40:40.660 --> 1:40:42.370
